  <original-body>Sanitize changes &amp;amp within a URI to &amp;amp;amp. This manifests when sanitize is invoked repeatedly on the same data.
Here's a test:

class TestController &lt; ApplicationController
  include ActionView::Helpers::SanitizeHelper

  def test
    @a = sanitize(sanitize(sanitize('&lt;a href=&quot;http://foo.com/?a=b&amp;c=d&amp;e=f&quot;&gt;testing&lt;/a&gt;')))
  end
end

The output is:
&quot;&lt;a href=\&quot;http://foo.com/?a=b&amp;amp;amp;amp;c=d&amp;amp;amp;amp;e=f\&quot;&gt;testing&lt;/a&gt;&quot;</original-body>
